summary: This is purely for anyone who wants to use this in a mod, it is not a new item it is only a model.
descriptionHtml:
This is only a model, if anyone wishes to use it in a mod then they a free to do so; it started off as me making an earpiece and then I got immensely off course, so here we are.

It\'s only a 5-10 minute model (not to mention I haven\'t used blender much) so don\'t expect Nobel Prize winning quality.
Not exceptional but will hopefully be acceptable.

Also the blue render was just me screwing around with nodes on blender (it doesn\'t look *that* good.)

Maybe I\'ll create another model but I wouldn\'t bet on it.

This model may be used freely, credit is not required but it would be nice to see if anyone used it (which I doubt.)
author: Ryugahta
